# 🖍️ Draw Overlay Tool

A lightweight tool that lets you draw directly on top of any webpage — like a transparent whiteboard layer.

## ✨ Features

- Draw on top of any webpage
- Erase, change color, and brush size
- Save your drawing as PNG
- Touch + mouse support
- Toggle on/off with one click

## 🔧 How to Use

1. Open `index.html` in your browser.
2. Click the **"Activate Drawing"** button.
3. Right-click to open the drawing tools menu.
4. Press **Escape** to exit.

